        <p class="tm-eyebrow">What we believe</p>
        <h2 class="tm-h2">Wellness with purpose</h2>
        <p class="tm-body" style="margin:0 auto;">We didn't set out to build another tea brand. We set out to re-engineer a daily ritual that respects your time and your body.</p>
        <div class="tm-about-values__grid">
          <div class="tm-about-values__card">
            <div class="tm-about-values__icon">🍃</div>
            <h3>Real ingredients</h3>
            <p>Whole spices, real tea leaves, hydrolyzed peptides. No "natural flavors" mystery blend. No fillers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tm-about-values__card">
            <div class="tm-about-values__icon">👨‍👩‍👧</div>
            <h3>Family heritage</h3>
            <p>Since 1935. Four generations of tea obsession. The same nose test, the same standard, four generations on.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tm-about-values__card">
            <div class="tm-about-values__icon">⚡</div>
