  </section>

  <!-- NARRATIVE — passion for tea -->
  <section class="tm-section tm-section--cream">
    <div class="tm-section__inner">
      <div class="tm-about-narrative">
        <div class="tm-about-narrative__media">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dcwxmxfau/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,w_1200/Copy_of_M2_cqojf2.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="tm-eyebrow">Our passion</p>
          <h2 class="tm-h2">Helping you battle the day with a little support</h2>
          <p class="tm-body">At TMolecule we want to share our passion for tea. Our goal is to make you re-discover this centuries-old drink with our modern take on timeless classics. We are committed to offering you a premium-tasting tea and the best aromas with every sip.</p>
          <p class="tm-body" style="margin-top:16px;">Spice Rush is what happens when four generations of tea obsession meet a modern life. We take a classic spiced black-tea ritual, mill the leaf so you can actually drink it in under a minute, and add collagen peptides so one cup earns its keep.</p>
