        <p class="tm-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">The long arc</p>
        <h2 class="tm-h2" style="text-align:center;">Ninety-one years in the making</h2>
        <ol class="tm-about-timeline__list">
          <li><span class="tm-about-timeline__year">1935</span><p>Great-grandfather sources his first tin of Assam black tea — tin by tin, estate by estate, refusing anything that didn't meet the nose test.</p></li>
          <li><span class="tm-about-timeline__year">1962</span><p>Second generation expands the family sourcing to Ceylon and Darjeeling estates. The tasting protocol becomes a written standard.</p></li>
