          <li><span class="tm-about-timeline__year">2025</span><p>Spice Rush formula finalized — bold milled black tea, collagen peptides, three warming spices. Ready for the modern morning.</p></li>
          <li><span class="tm-about-timeline__year">2026</span><p>TMolecule launches direct-to-consumer. The ritual is now yours.</p></li>
