    <div class="tm-about-signature">
      <blockquote>"Good tea shouldn't need a strainer, a timer, and a degree in horology. It should need you."</blockquote>
      <cite>— The TMolecule family</cite>
      <div style="margin-top:48px;"><a href="/products/premium-collagen-spice-rush-black-tea-blend-revitalizing-energy-with-ginger-cinnamon-cardamom-keto-paleo-friendly-made-in-usa-milled-product-for-smoother-flow" class="tm-btn">Start Your Ritual<span class="tm-btn__sub">$6.99 · free shipping over $35</span></a></div>
    </div>
